{
  "id": "6a13af0b9958bbfbe9b82618",
  "title": "2026/05/25 おかゆ",
  "created": 1779674893,
  "updated": 1779733624,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a13af0b9958bbfbe9b82618",
      "text": "2026/05/25 おかゆ",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1779674893,
      "updated": 1779675528
    },
    {
      "id": "6a13af90000000000059605a",
      "text": "[井戸端日記 お粥]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1779675025,
      "updated": 1779675025
    },
    {
      "id": "6a13af91000000000059605b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1779675026,
      "updated": 1779675026
    },
    {
      "id": "6a13af120000000000596057",
      "text": "[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1779674898,
      "updated": 1779674899
    },
    {
      "id": "6a13af0d0000000000596055",
      "text": " おなかがすいたので昨日漬けた味玉を食べた",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1779674893,
      "updated": 1779674912
    },
    {
      "id": "6a13d46700000000001626ab",
      "text": " 冷やしトマトウマー🍅",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1779684456,
      "updated": 1779684463
    },
    {
      "id": "6a141fcb00000000009e8ba7",
      "text": " \tいいなあ[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1779703755,
      "updated": 1779703756
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1426fc000000000027ef4e",
      "text": " カレーのことを考えている",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1779705597,
      "updated": 1779705602
    },
    {
      "id": "6a142bf700000000007df4f9",
      "text": "  いろいろ考えたが、求めるカレーと入手可能なカレーとの差異が大きく、カレーを諦めた",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1779706872,
      "updated": 1779706904
    },
    {
      "id": "6a13af0f0000000000596056",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1779674896,
      "updated": 1779674896
    },
    {
      "id": "6a13af150000000000ad5aff",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779674912,
      "updated": 1779674913
    },
    {
      "id": "6a13af170000000000ad5b01",
      "text": "\tごはんたべてくる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779674913,
      "updated": 1779674916
    },
    {
      "id": "6a13bd3d0000000000c0cd7b",
      "text": "\t[お粥]よりもおつゆを混ぜた重湯のほうが好き",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1779678526,
      "updated": 1779719292
    },
    {
      "id": "6a13bd650000000000c0cd7c",
      "text": "\t\t[飲むうどん]みたいな味がする",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1779678566,
      "updated": 1779700284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1433590000000000c08068",
      "text": "\t緩い話をしようとしたら食べ物の話になってしまう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1779708762,
      "updated": 1779708779
    },
    {
      "id": "6a13af8b0000000000596059",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1779675020,
      "updated": 1779675020
    },
    {
      "id": "6a13afa40000000000e45cf1",
      "text": "[wogikaze.icon]",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1779675046,
      "updated": 1779675047
    },
    {
      "id": "6a13afa50000000000e45cf3",
      "text": " 漢字おおいので「[おかゆ]」にしないか",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1779675047,
      "updated": 1779675546
    },
    {
      "id": "6a13afc00000000000e45cf4",
      "text": " やわいほうが",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1779675074,
      "updated": 1779675077
    },
    {
      "id": "6a13afa40000000000e45cf2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1779675047,
      "updated": 1779675047
    },
    {
      "id": "6a13afed0000000000c41cd2",
      "text": "[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1779675115,
      "updated": 1779675115
    },
    {
      "id": "6a13afed0000000000c41cd4",
      "text": " 入院数日はぜんがゆ食べてたけど、胃の調子が戻ってからはじょうしょくに変えてもらった",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1779675115,
      "updated": 1779675144
    },
    {
      "id": "6a13afed0000000000c41cd3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1779675115,
      "updated": 1779675115
    },
    {
      "id": "6a13b02e0000000000979de5",
      "text": "[koyoshi.icon]",
      "userId": "6606ca1148e7150024f0f07d",
      "created": 1779675182,
      "updated": 1779675183
    },
    {
      "id": "6a13b0300000000000979de7",
      "text": " お茶を買いに行ってる間に何か生えてた！",
      "userId": "6606ca1148e7150024f0f07d",
      "created": 1779675184,
      "updated": 1779675202
    },
    {
      "id": "6a13b06c0000000000979de8",
      "text": "  [フッ軽]すごいな",
      "userId": "6606ca1148e7150024f0f07d",
      "created": 1779675244,
      "updated": 1779675263
    },
    {
      "id": "6a13f81300000000002bb836",
      "text": " 眠かったので[緑のモンスターのエキス]を飲んだ",
      "userId": "6606ca1148e7150024f0f07d",
      "created": 1779693588,
      "updated": 1779693614
    },
    {
      "id": "6a13b02f0000000000979de6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6606ca1148e7150024f0f07d",
      "created": 1779675183,
      "updated": 1779675183
    },
    {
      "id": "6a13b2990000000000ce6c10",
      "text": "[Hiro Aki.icon]",
      "userId": "65e1289acd012200235729c0",
      "created": 1779675802,
      "updated": 1779675804
    },
    {
      "id": "6a13b29c0000000000ce6c12",
      "text": "\t昨日の昼ごはんはお茶漬けだった。[永谷園のお茶漬け]は世界最強だと思う",
      "userId": "65e1289acd012200235729c0",
      "created": 1779675804,
      "updated": 1779675824
    },
    {
      "id": "6a13b29c0000000000ce6c11",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "65e1289acd012200235729c0",
      "created": 1779675804,
      "updated": 1779675804
    },
    {
      "id": "6a13b2a30000000000cf04c0",
      "text": "[nyarla.icon]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1779675811,
      "updated": 1779675812
    },
    {
      "id": "6a13b2a40000000000cf04c2",
      "text": "\t小腹がすいたのでキットカット抹茶味をもぐもぐ",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1779675812,
      "updated": 1779675837
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1411ea0000000000830b0d",
      "text": "\t今日の夕食はカレーです",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1779700203,
      "updated": 1779700215
    },
    {
      "id": "6a141216000000000063e947",
      "text": "\t カレーの口になってきた[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1779700247,
      "updated": 1779700253
    },
    {
      "id": "6a13b2a40000000000cf04c1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1779675812,
      "updated": 1779675812
    },
    {
      "id": "6a13b56b000000000049eedb",
      "text": "[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1779676524,
      "updated": 1779676524
    },
    {
      "id": "6a13b56c000000000049eedd",
      "text": "\tねちがえたっぽいねん。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1779676524,
      "updated": 1779676529
    },
    {
      "id": "6a141ee2000000000088d8b7",
      "text": "\tきのうから、いつもの気圧系の頭痛だったことに、さっき思いいたった",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1779703523,
      "updated": 1779703555
    },
    {
      "id": "6a145b850000000000684d50",
      "text": "\tむげんぴーまんつくった。むげんにたべた。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1779719046,
      "updated": 1779719059
    },
    {
      "id": "6a145b9a0000000000684d51",
      "text": "\t卵を白身と黄身に分けようと慎重に割ったらグシャっとなっちゃった[(´；ω；｀)]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1779719067,
      "updated": 1779719135
    },
    {
      "id": "6a145c3d000000000017b67b",
      "text": "\t耳の奥をﾊｧｯ!!!ってやったら耳がよくなった",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1779719230,
      "updated": 1779719242
    },
    {
      "id": "6a146df00000000000f83a8c",
      "text": "\t[えるしっているか]せっけんについたけはけつでふくととれるぞ",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1779723761,
      "updated": 1779723797
    },
    {
      "id": "6a13b56c000000000049eedc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1779676524,
      "updated": 1779676524
    },
    {
      "id": "6a13c2650000000000ccdc9c",
      "text": "[zatsma.icon]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1779679846,
      "updated": 1779679848
    },
    {
      "id": "6a13c2670000000000ccdc9e",
      "text": " 妻が食中毒っぽくなったときに生まれて初めて重湯を作ったことがある",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1779679848,
      "updated": 1779680150
    },
    {
      "id": "6a13c27a0000000000ccdc9f",
      "text": "  「え、こんな量しかできないの」と思った",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1779679867,
      "updated": 1779679889
    },
    {
      "id": "6a14460a0000000000c69cfb",
      "text": " 卵サンドをたべた",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1779713547,
      "updated": 1779713553
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1412020000000000fc817e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1779700226,
      "updated": 1779700227
    },
    {
      "id": "6a13c2650000000000ccdc9d",
      "text": "[taktamur.icon]",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1779679846,
      "updated": 1779700224
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1412000000000000fc817d",
      "text": " [蒟蒻畑]をつまむ",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1779700224,
      "updated": 1779700320
    },
    {
      "id": "6a14120d0000000000fc817f",
      "text": "  腹回りがアレでアレしまして。。",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1779700238,
      "updated": 1779700272
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1412410000000000fc8180",
      "text": "  こんにゃくは消化的にはあまりよろしくないらしい(LLM調べ)",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1779700289,
      "updated": 1779700310
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1412980000000000c34891",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "67bf02ec874ae1ce04e71b08",
      "created": 1779700376,
      "updated": 1779700376
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1412a00000000000c34893",
      "text": "[onuma.icon]",
      "userId": "67bf02ec874ae1ce04e71b08",
      "created": 1779700383,
      "updated": 1779700385
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1412980000000000c34892",
      "text": " お腹空いたので帰る",
      "userId": "67bf02ec874ae1ce04e71b08",
      "created": 1779700376,
      "updated": 1779700387
    },
    {
      "id": "6a141a8c0000000000f0ce03",
      "text": " なにたべよー",
      "userId": "67bf02ec874ae1ce04e71b08",
      "created": 1779702412,
      "updated": 1779702415
    },
    {
      "id": "6a14394800000000000bc98b",
      "text": " ケバブを食べた",
      "userId": "67bf02ec874ae1ce04e71b08",
      "created": 1779710280,
      "updated": 1779710284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1411ff0000000000fc817c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1779700224,
      "updated": 1779700224
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1445a800000000006cbdfb",
      "text": "[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1779713449,
      "updated": 1779713452
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1445ac00000000006cbdfd",
      "text": "　さいきんにっきがいかつすぎる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1779713453,
      "updated": 1779713462
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1445b600000000006cbdfe",
      "text": "　つかれてまして",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1779713462,
      "updated": 1779713476
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1445e700000000006cbdff",
      "text": "　ねこは便秘になって医者におしりをほじられてうんこを3つ取り出されたら精神的ショックを受けたらしくて凹んでた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1779713512,
      "updated": 1779713610
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1445ac00000000006cbdfc",
      "text": "　　まあ、自分が「自分の体重の10倍以上あるでかい生き物」におしりをほじられたらどう思うかと想像すると(遠い目)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1779713452,
      "updated": 1779713737
    },
    {
      "id": "6a145cdd0000000000051146",
      "text": "　　猫って凹むんだ[yosider.icon][takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1779719388,
      "updated": 1779733624
    },
    {
      "id": "6a14468a00000000006cbe00",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1779713674,
      "updated": 1779713674
    },
    {
      "id": "6a144a1000000000001f529d",
      "text": "[atohs.icon]",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1779714577,
      "updated": 1779714580
    },
    {
      "id": "6a144a1300000000001f529f",
      "text": " ごぼうが10kgくらいあり、どうしようかかんがえています",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1779714580,
      "updated": 1779714594
    },
    {
      "id": "6a144a1100000000001f529e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1779714577,
      "updated": 1779714577
    },
    {
      "id": "6a144fcc0000000000243654",
      "text": "[hoshihara.icon]",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1779716043,
      "updated": 1779716044
    },
    {
      "id": "6a144fcd0000000000243656",
      "text": "\tうちにもじゃがいもが大量にあり連日じゃがいも料理を頂いている",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1779716044,
      "updated": 1779716055
    },
    {
      "id": "6a144fdc0000000000243657",
      "text": "\t今日はにくじゃが食べた",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1779716060,
      "updated": 1779716064
    },
    {
      "id": "6a144fe10000000000243658",
      "text": "\tああ",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1779716064,
      "updated": 1779716096
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1450010000000000243659",
      "text": "\tゲーム消したらつまんなくなったのでゲーム入れよう",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1779716096,
      "updated": 1779716104
    },
    {
      "id": "6a144fcc0000000000243655",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1779716044,
      "updated": 1779716044
    }
  ]
}